                <mxCell id="173" value="&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 24px;&quot;&gt;Concern cargo version&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;font-size: 18px;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;- Waypoint planning&amp;nbsp;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(192, 192, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: light-dark(rgb(192, 192, 192), rgb(72, 72, 72)); background-color: transparent; font-weight: bold; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)&quot;&gt;- mission waypoint at point B is always adjust -&amp;gt; &lt;u&gt;so both pilot will be safely check and comfirm for flying safe and&amp;nbsp;&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; scrollbar-color: rgb(75, 75, 75) rgb(27, 29, 30); color: rgb(192, 192, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(192, 192, 192); scrollbar-color: rgb(75, 75, 75) rgb(27, 29, 30);&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(192, 192, 192); scrollbar-color: rgb(75, 75, 75) rgb(27, 29, 30); white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;make sure select exist mission (to hover when finish mission)&lt;/u&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: rgb(192, 192, 192); font-size: medium; background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: rgb(192, 192, 192); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- following procedure, if pilot 2 use reverse mission path when loading finish maybe it will uncomfortable -&amp;gt; &lt;u&gt;Pre-plan &lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;text-decoration-line: underline; background-color: transparent; scrollbar-color: rgb(75, 75, 75) rgb(27, 29, 30); color: rgb(192, 192, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;color: rgb(192, 192, 192); scrollbar-color: rgb(75, 75, 75) rgb(27, 29, 30);&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(192, 192, 192); scrollbar-color: rgb(75, 75, 75) rgb(27, 29, 30); white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;from delivery hub &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(192, 192, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;may be better . &lt;/u&gt; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: rgb(192, 192, 192); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Payload weight &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: rgb(192, 192, 192); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;&lt;font style=&quot;&quot; size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-weight: bold; white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;b&gt;- &lt;u&gt;maximum allowed payload may be less than 10 kg&lt;/u&gt;. cause from test range 20,25 kg, fly from h1 to airplane and airplane to h1 battery is in critical zone. In case when real use if drone already receive payload from FSO&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(192, 192, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;but can&#39;t land on BQP (by some reason) it must have remaining battery to fly to FSO again.   &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(192, 192, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- size of payload must be fitted in cargo.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(192, 192, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Drone speed &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(192, 192, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;-&lt;u&gt; recommended 10 m/s&lt;/u&gt; as all test with drone speed 10 m/s &lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(192, 192, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;- Updated home &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(192, 192, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;- due to use gps from remote to updated home position, average error is 3-4 meters. -&amp;gt; &lt;u&gt;When updated home pilot will be stand at target point and waiting a few seconds(20-30 sec) before press updated home. &lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(192, 192, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;u&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;And if drone in land in target, pilot must take control to land. &lt;/u&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: left;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;background-color: transparent; color: rgb(192, 192, 192);&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space-collapse: preserve;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&#x9;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;" style="text;html=1;align=center;verticalAlign=middle;resizable=0;points=[];autosize=1;strokeColor=none;fillColor=none;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="200" y="1320" width="1700" height="320" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
