eive payload from FSO&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; scrollbar-color: rgb(75, 75, 75) rgb(27, 29, 30); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: nowrap; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: left; color: rgb(192, 192, 192); background-color: rgb(27, 29, 30); box-shadow: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; scrollbar-color: rgb(75, 75, 75) rgb(27, 29, 30); color: rgb(192, 192, 192); box-shadow: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=&quot;rgba(0, 0, 0, 0)&quot; size=&quot;3&quot; style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; scrollbar-color: rgb(75, 75, 75) rgb(27, 29, 30); color: rgb(192, 192, 192); box-shadow: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; scrollbar-color: rgb(75, 75, 75) rgb(27, 29, 30); white-space-collapse: preserve; color: rgb(192, 192, 192); box-shadow: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; scrollbar-color: rgb(75, 75, 75) rgb(27, 29, 30); white-space: pre; color: rgb(192, 192, 192); box-shadow: none !important;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;white-space: pre;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;but can&#39;t land on BQP (by some reason) it must have remaining battery to fly to FSO again.   &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div style=&quot;forced-color-adjust: none; scrollbar-color: rgb(75, 75, 75) rgb(27, 29, 30); font-family: Helvetica; font-size: 12px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-